title: Ebro In The Morning - Joyner Lucas Squashes His Beef With Rosenberg + App Development
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Joyner Lucas stepped up to Ebro in the Morning to discuss a variety of topics including his family's reaction to his breakout track 'I'm Not Racist', his relationship w/ J. Cole, being respected as an artist and more.

He also discusses his disagreements with Karen Civil, Steve Stoute, and even roasts Rosenberg a bit on their former issues and the origin of them. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
